# Notes:
# - Channel index maps to iChannelN (0 = iChannel0, 1 = iChannel1, etc.)
# - Use default texture names for procedural textures (no file I/O)
# - Use absolute or relative file paths for custom images
# - "_" means skip/empty channel (no texture bound)
# - If channels array is not specified, defaults are used for all 5 channels
